// ==============================================================================
// KEY FEATURES DEMONSTRATED IN v0.0.4:
// ==============================================================================
// ✓ INDENTATION: 3-space nesting (no \~\ markers)
// ✓ BOOLEAN OPS: [&], [|], [^] with indentation
// ✓ MATCH EXPR: [m] block with [?] cases and ? operator
// ✓ COMPOSITION: |> operator for pipeline chaining
// ✓ STRUCT LITERALS: [.] fields with indentation (no {})
// ✓ SIMPLIFIED BRACKETS: [<] and [>] instead of [<} and [>}
// ✓ COMMA VARIABLES: ,variable for all variables/parameters
// ✓ DOT HIERARCHY: Universal separator for all constructs
//   - Variables: ,var.field.subfield
//   - Types: :pg.array.pg.string (no curly braces!)
//   - Enums: #Type.Value
//   - Pipelines: |Namespace.Pipeline
//   - Errors: !Category.Domain.Error
// ✓ TYPE HIERARCHY: Full dot notation (e.g., :pg.array.pg.error)
// ✓ NO NESTED ARRAYS: Use :pg.array.pg.serial for complex nested data
// ✓ CLEAN SYNTAX: Dramatically reduced visual noise
// ✓ UNIVERSAL PATTERN: PREFIX.identifier.hierarchy.path
// ==============================================================================
